# BD Freight Partners Recruitment Funnel

## Overview
This project is a freight partner recruitment and lead intake funnel built to support owner-operator recruiting.

It includes a pre-qualification flow, a full application flow, compliance pages for messaging, and serverless backend handling for applicant submissions.

## Tech Stack
- Netlify for hosting and serverless functions
- Twilio for SMS campaign setup and messaging workflows
- Resend for transactional email delivery
- Cloudflare for DNS, security, performance, and bot protection

## Features
- Owner-operator landing and routing flow
- Pre-qualification flow
- Full application flow
- Thank-you and redirect handling
- Privacy Policy and Terms pages for messaging compliance
- Cloudflare Turnstile bot protection
- Netlify Functions for backend form processing and email delivery

## Current Status
- Twilio campaign submitted for review
- Compliance pages are live and accessible
- Recruitment funnel is deployed and functional
- Repository has been cleaned and organized for professional review

## Next Steps
- Move prequal and application flows into the Lanetool system
- Add lead tracking and workflow status management
- Improve validation and modular structure
- Expand compliance content as needed

## Project Purpose
This repository serves as the public-facing recruitment funnel for BD Freight Partners.

It is designed to capture applicant interest, qualify owner-operators, and support compliant follow-up communication while a deeper Lanetool workflow is developed separately.

